description:
Danny welcomes Becca Tobin from the Ladygang podcast & Glee to talk about her upcoming book, her Bravo hot-takes, and lots more! Dan Lanigan from Disney+'s Prop Culture also stops by to discuss the amazing new series, hopes for season 2, films that stand the test of time and more!


Becca Tobin: 3:00ish

Dan Lanigan: 24:29ish


Watch these interviews & more at www.YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
